<bibRefCitation author="Tserkova, F. &amp; Klisarova, D. &amp; Denev, I." box="[655,888,619,646]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" pagination="241 - 246" refId="ref65579" refString="Tserkova, F., Klisarova, D. &amp; Denev, I. (2016) Molecular taxonomy study of representatives of the genus Gobius inhabiting coastal waters of Black Sea region. Journal of BioScience and Biotechnology, 5 (3), 241 - 246." type="journal article" year="2016">
